snippet.title: ATOMIC PICNIC - Summer Games Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1903560/Atomic_Picnic/
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/Bitcake

ATOMIC PICNIC is a co-op third-person shooter roguelite!
Get together with up to 4 friends to fight hordes of monsters, gain experience to upgrade your weapons, and create the best build possible to survive. Every Picnic is different, each containing a variety of upgrades that can radically change how you play!

Join the Stalkers today at...
🌎 https://playatomicpicnic.com
📷 https://instagr.am/BitCake.Studio
